{
  "texts": [
    "Kavipriya and Sengaliappan (2021) proposed a Deep Learning Decision Support System (DLDSS) prediction model that demonstrates the potential of data mining using DL techniques for estimating the total student performance in college placements.",
    "An Adaptive Weight Deep Convolutional Neural Network (AWDCNN) classifier was utilized to model the DLDSS prediction algorithm.",
    "To estimate the student performance, an AWDCNN is utilized, which is based on a feed-forward NN that generates precise prediction values.",
    "The classifier's weights were regularized using the GA method.",
    "In addition, the prediction was enhanced by using adaptive weights as opposed to conventional fixed weights."
  ]
}